{"tid":1246071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西伯利亞潮文反送中版","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T14:53:33.000Z","uid":41058,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a19570a366e57cd4739030b0a152e9748c580c","tid":1246071,"uid":41058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"一萬人聯署抗議，荷蘭政府撤回爭議方案，香港政府指有充份咨詢；<br />\n五萬人上街，英國國會召開緊急會議，香港政府指制度行之有效；<br />\n廿萬人遊行，澳洲內閣集體請辭，香港政府話和平遊行係香港常見活動；<br />\n一百萬人遊行，德國警察倒戈支持市民，香港政府話方案有急切性必需儘快執行；<br />\n全市醞釀罷市罷課，法國市民發表革命宣言，香港警察抱怨市民戴防護裝備打得唔夠開心；<br />\n二百萬人遊行，美國開始陷入內戰，林鄭月娥終於說：「政府做得唔夠好，對唔撚住囉，不過我唔會撤回」"},{"pid":"699e0a487277df7cec42a0f1343de4b907800546","tid":1246071,"uid":212119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a90ac6f07fe73f4f01fb8e44ad595de965230e","tid":1246071,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"cd2a345e1d7326330e34afc514b923124b7cc24d","tid":1246071,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"喊出黎"},{"pid":"a9fa4cffc94422e632966004d3d7def0fca6b0fb","tid":1246071,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ff2553680ddea2b5ac7eb2f18d6067654f2ff6a","tid":1246071,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fefa859a8e171c1554541a0949bd8a75e0affaa","tid":1246071,"uid":133183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2